display: none;\">\n                        <p>This website processes all images locally in your browser. No image data is stored on my servers during normal operation.</p>\n                        <p>When using the sharing function, images are temporarily processed through my server to facilitate uploading to catbox.moe (see their <a href=\"https://catbox.moe/legal.php\">Privacy Policy</a>. These images are not stored on my servers and are immediately forwarded.</p>\n                        <p>The site uses a session cookie for technical functionality. No other cookies are set, and I do not collect personal data or tracking information.</p>\n                        <p>Last updated: 7 February 2025</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"menu-row\"><a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/C0C51A829H\" class=\"image-link\" target=\"_blank\"><img height=\"36\" style=\"border:0px;height:36px;\" src=\"/img/kofi6.webp\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Buy Me a Coffee at ko-fi.com\"></a></div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div></div></div></div><div class=\"simplebar-placeholder\" style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px;\"></div></div><div class=\"simplebar-track simplebar-horizontal\" style=\"visibility: hidden;\"><div class=\"simplebar-scrollbar\" style=\"width: 0px; display: none;\"></div></div><div class=\"simplebar-track simplebar-vertical\" style=\"visibility: hidden;\"><div class=\"simplebar-scrollbar\" style=\"height: 0px; display: none;\"></div></div></div>\n\n    </div>\n    <script async=\"\" src=\"https://scripts.simpleanalyticscdn.com/latest.js\"></script>\n\n</body></html>",
